OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe government is planning a number of
OL,8,Freforms to the SEND (special
OL,9,Feducational needs and disabilities)
OL,10,Fsystem, which could be revealed in a
OL,11,Fwhite paper as early as Monday.
OL,13,FLeaked details suggest that from 2029,
OL,14,Fchildren with SEND will face having
OL,15,Ftheir right to support under an
OL,16,FEducation, Health and Care Plan (EHCP)
OL,17,Freviewed when they reach the end of
OL,18,Fprimary school.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
