OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe reforms are expected to introduce
OL,8,Fa plan with legal footing for all
OL,9,Fchildren with SEND called Individual
OL,10,FSupport Plans (ISPs).
OL,12,FAhead of the publication of the
OL,13,FSchools White Paper, ITV News takes a
OL,14,Flook at the key data behind the SEND
OL,15,Fcrisis.
OL,17,FWhat is the scale of SEND need?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
