OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FOver 1.7 million pupils in England
OL,8,Fhave special educational needs. That
OL,9,Fequates to nearly one in every six
OL,10,Fschool age children - at nearly 15%.
OL,12,FAround 5% of these have an education,
OL,13,Fhealth and care plan (EHCP), which is
OL,14,Fthe highest level of SEND support
OL,15,Favailable.
OL,17,FEHCP's are documents which detail the
OL,18,Flevel and type of support a child
OL,19,Fneeds. They are legally binding,
OL,20,Fmeaning any child with one is entitled
OL,21,Fto extra provision by law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
