OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSince 2018, the number of children and
OL,8,Fyoung people supported by an EHCP has
OL,9,Fnearly doubled. The majority of these
OL,10,F(483,000) are of school age.
OL,12,FThe latest official figures show that
OL,13,Fnearly 640,000 children and young
OL,14,Fpeople aged under 25 had an active
OL,15,FEHCP plan as of January 2026. In 2018,
OL,16,Fthat figure was much lower - at
OL,17,F354,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
