OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FExperts say the increase has largely
OL,8,Fbeen driven by more children with
OL,9,Fdiagnosis of autism and ADHD getting
OL,10,Fthe highest level of support.
OL,12,FAs of 2025, the most common reason for
OL,13,Fchildren having an EHCP was autistic
OL,14,Fspectrum disorder.
OL,16,FAnd with this, a significant increase
OL,17,Fin children needing support has
OL,18,Fsignificantly increased costs.
OL,20,FHow much is spent on SEND?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
