OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe way that schools receive and spend
OL,8,FSEND funding is determined by a
OL,9,Fcomplex formula.
OL,11,FSchools must fund the first chunk of
OL,12,Fsupport for a pupil with special
OL,13,Fneeds, up to a cap of #6,000.
OL,15,FAfter that, any further costs -
OL,16,Fincluding EHCP costs - are covered by
OL,17,Fsomething called 'high needs funding'
OL,18,F- which is sent to councils by central
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
