OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FCouncils are projected to spend over
OL,8,F#14.8bn on this type of SEND support
OL,9,Fthis year.
OL,11,FThe chart above, made using data from
OL,12,Fthe Institute for Fiscal Studies and
OL,13,FOffice for Budget Responsibility,
OL,14,Fshows how sharply this spending has
OL,15,Fincreased - from #7.8bn in 2015, to
OL,16,F#9.3bn in 2020, to a record #14.8bn
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,19,FThere has been a particular focus on
OL,20,Fthe increased cost in certain types of
OL,21,FSEND support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
