OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,8,Fbroke down what was behind the growth
OL,9,Fin 'high needs' spending.
OL,11,FThe think-tank found that council
OL,12,Fspending on private special schools -
OL,13,Ffee-paying schools for pupils with
OL,14,Fadditional needs - had grown by 92%
OL,15,Fsince 2018.
OL,17,FPlacements in private special schools
OL,18,Fcost on average #60,000 a year,
OL,19,Faccording to a 2024 report by National
OL,20,FAudit Office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
