OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FOnly around 6% of pupils with an EHCP
OL,8,Fare placed in this kind of school, but
OL,9,Fthey cost councils nearly #2bn in
OL,10,Ftotal.
OL,12,FCosts for transport to take kids with
OL,13,Fspecial needs to school have also
OL,14,Fsoared, increasing by 81% over the
OL,15,Flast 7 years. ITV News has previously
OL,16,Freported on the impact of rising
OL,17,Ftransport costs on councils.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
