OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FIn a report published on Thursday, the
OL,8,FCounty Councils Network warned that
OL,9,Fcouncils are now spending close to
OL,10,F#10,000 on average to get one SEND
OL,11,Fpupil to school.
OL,13,FThey warned school transport costs for
OL,14,FSEND children could hit #3.4bn by 2030/
OL,15,F31.
OL,17,FAccording to the IFS, SEND transport
OL,18,Fcosts have already hit #2bn in total.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
