OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMany SEND kids have to travel far away
OL,8,Ffrom home to attend school, often
OL,9,Fbecause of a lack of suitable school
OL,10,Fplaces in their community.
OL,12,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,13,Fhas said ballooning transport costs is
OL,14,Fsomething her new SEND strategy will
OL,15,Faddress.
OL,17,FThe amount of money supporting SEND
OL,18,Fkids in mainstream schools has also
OL,19,Fincreased by 72% since 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
