OL,3,COver #2bn spent taking children to
OL,4,Cschool: The numbers behind the SEND
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FBecause in order to bring down SEND
OL,8,Fspending, Philipson will not only have
OL,9,Fto reduce the number of SEND kids
OL,10,Fgoing to out-of-catchment placements,
OL,11,For expensive private schools.
OL,13,FShe will have reform how SEND
OL,14,Fprovision is delivered in mainstream
OL,15,Fschools as well.
OL,17,FThe soaring SEND costs are such that
OL,18,Fmany councils have had to dip into
OL,19,Ftheir main school funding pot to top
OL,20,Fup their special needs support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
