OL,7,FThe grant will be called the 'High
OL,8,FNeeds Stability Grant'.
OL,10,FAfter that point, SEND spending will
OL,11,Fbe absorbed into central government, a
OL,12,Fchange which was announced by the
OL,13,Fchancellor in November.
OL,15,FIt's not yet clear how the education
OL,16,Fsecretary will fund this rescue
OL,17,Fpackage, or what the impact of the
OL,18,Fremaining 10% debt will be on council
OL,19,Fbudgets - but many council leaders
OL,20,Fwelcomed the move.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
