OL,8,Fthere is fear that this extra
OL,9,Fgovernment finance could come with
OL,10,F"strings attached".
OL,12,FAnd that the need to pay back the
OL,13,Fremaining 10% of debt could force
OL,14,Fcouncils into cost-cutting, which
OL,15,Fcould lead to poorer provision for
OL,16,Ftheir kids.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
